{"tid":2374183,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"流浮山160呎貨櫃屋月租$2400包水費WiFi　網民︰裝修好過劏房","createTime":"2021-01-21T05:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T10:08:57.000Z","uid":271829,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"c437007740d43b74b33efe60ac91ce02c1586b58","tid":2374183,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2855000/2858398/house_thumb_20210121_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2855000%2F2858398%2Fhouse_thumb_20210121_S_1024.jpg&h=9be67f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 流浮山有一間160呎貨櫃屋放租，月租僅2,400元。<br />\n<br />\n香港地少人多，樓價冠絕全球，港人想擁有一個小天地非常艱難。近日facebook有一個「另類租盤」引起網民關注，該個位於流浮山的160呎貨櫃屋，雖然外表簡陋，但內裡已有裝修，家具齊備，且包水費及WIFI設備，租金僅2,400元，網民對此反應不一。<br />\n有網民日前於facebook「自己物業自己放，租買免佣」發帖文，放租位於流浮山白泥村一間貨櫃屋，鄰近流浮山廈村鄉已遭「殺校」的白坭公立學校。貨櫃屋面積160呎，月租2400元，已包水費及WIFI。<br />\n該處放租者介紹指，有村巴出入元朗，途經天水圍西鐵站；駕車人士則可在深圳灣前最後一個出口，經雞伯嶺路進入，只需約5至10分鐘車程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2855000/2858398/house_05_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2855000%2F2858398%2Fhouse_05_1024.jpg&h=d55aea74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貨櫃屋的外觀較殘舊。（facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2855000/2858398/house_02_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2855000%2F2858398%2Fhouse_02_1024.jpg&h=a829ec2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家具以白色為主，尚算齊備。（facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2855000/2858398/house_03_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2855000%2F2858398%2Fhouse_03_1024.jpg&h=75bf35a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內有浴室，更有摺門將廳一分為二。（facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2855000/2858398/house_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2855000%2F2858398%2Fhouse_01_1024.jpg&h=15e380e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外面有空地放有植物。（facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2855000/2858398/house_04_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2855000%2F2858398%2Fhouse_04_1024.jpg&h=08cc33f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交通地圖。（facebook圖片）<br />\n<br />\n從相片中可見，貨櫃屋黃色的外觀比較殘舊，但內裡裝修企理，空間不太擠迫，有廁所及淋浴設備，家具則以白色為主，睡床﹑梳化﹑飯桌連椅﹑小型儲物櫃﹑雪櫃及風扇等，算是應有盡有。中間更有摺門分隔客廳和「睡房」，佈置略有心思。<br />\n截稿前原帖已遭刪除，但在facebook買賣平台仍可見到，還列明內有冷氣設備，且門前加設了一排竹枝屏風，以遮擋大門和窗戶。屋外還有一個小空地及放有植物，讓人有喘息空間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2855000/2858398/house_07_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2855000%2F2858398%2Fhouse_07_1024.jpg&h=b5065f3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該租盤在facebook仍能見到。（facebook圖片）"},{"pid":"bdada54bd9e8b0c5f0bdda983de41c03d6cb45bb","tid":2374183,"uid":226466,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:02:58.000Z","msg":"抵租<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43e4b759c78e7dd8fa0a8ae05384e6994af30d9","tid":2374183,"uid":359522,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"拎來放Hottoys .... 抵過擺迷你倉"},{"pid":"6967230f8989609676f7c588511b6eaa2ac1ca8d","tid":2374183,"uid":32691,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"部冷氣夏天一定唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif